  in my home state the real estate industry is at an incipient stage  the real estate regulatory authority in each state can be made through the decisions of the state government  constitution grants sikkim a very special status  it is my hope that the autonomy of the state in this matter related to land  and  real  estate  will  be  maintained  to  allow  for  the  inclusion  of  special circumstances in each state especially those in the himalayan region  